</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-64_ pf-text-1"><strong>Utilising ComplyPlus™ software</strong> - Implementing ComplyPlus™ legislation and regulatory compliance management software can streamline compliance processes within educational institutions. This software helps manage and monitor adherence to relevant legislation, ensuring that institutions meet their statutory obligations efficiently.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-66_ pf-text-1"><strong>Promoting Continuous Professional Development</strong> - Institutions should encourage their staff to participate in CPD programmes offered by the NEU. This not only enhances the professional skills of educators but also ensures that they are well-equipped to handle the dynamic demands of the educational environment.











